class JumpScale.baselib.credis.CRedisQueue.CRedisQueue(redis, name, namespace='queue')[source]¶

Bases: object

Simple Queue with Redis Backend

empty()[source]¶

Return True if the queue is empty, False otherwise.

fetch(block=True, timeout=None)[source]¶

Like get but without remove

get(block=True, timeout=None)[source]¶

Remove and return an item from the queue.

If optional args block is true and timeout is None (the default), block if necessary until an item is available.

get_nowait()[source]¶

Equivalent to get(False).

put(item)[source]¶
